      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is the perfect 'diamond in the rough' project you've been searching for. While it currently requires a complete mechanical overhaul and significant cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to bring a classic back to life or use it for high-quality parts. Grab this project at an accessible price and start your next automotive adventure today!",
