    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-fresh appearance. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professionally applied multi-stage ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolstering wear, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, showing no signs of road debris or corrosion. We welcome and encourage any independent pre-purchase inspection at a shop of your choice to verify this vehicle's exceptional state. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
